### ========================================
### 截图1组：未携带 Token 被拦截（401）
### ========================================

### 1-A. DELETE 未携带 Token → 应被拦截，返回 401
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1001
Accept: application/json

###

### 1-B. PUT 未携带 Token → 应被拦截，返回 401
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "李四",
  "age": 22
}

###

### ========================================
### 截图2组：携带 Token 成功获取 JSON 数据（200）
### ========================================

### 2-A. DELETE 携带 Token → 应放行，返回 200
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mock-token-abc123

###

### 2-B. PUT 携带 Token → 应放行，返回 200
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mock-token-abc123

{
  "name": "李四",
  "age": 22
}

###

### ========================================
### 截图3组：无需 Token 直接放行的接口
### ========================================

### 3-A. 登录接口（WebConfig 路径放行）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "age": 21
}

###

### 3-B. 注册接口（拦截器内 POST 动词放行）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1001,
  "name": "张三",
  "age": 21
}

###

### 3-C. 查看用户信息（拦截器内 GET 动词放行）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1001
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### 附加：异常处理测试
### ========================================

### 4. 触发异常拦截测试（验证全局异常处理器）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/error
Accept: application/json
